OL,3,CMan who set up traps and explosives
OL,4,C'inspired by Home Alone'
OL,6,FA man accused of rigging his house
OL,7,Fwith tripwires attached to explosives
OL,8,Fto protect his drugs business told
OL,9,Fpolice he was inspired by the classic
OL,10,F1990 comedy movie Home Alone, a court
OL,11,Fhas heard.
OL,13,FDoncaster Crown Court heard that
OL,14,Faround 100 homes in Grimethorpe, near
OL,15,FBarnsley, were evacuated in the former
OL,16,Fpit village in May 2024 after police
OL,17,Fexecuted warrants at three
OL,18,Fneighbouring houses connected to Ian
OL,19,Fand Lesley
OL,21,FClaughton in Brierley Road.
