OL,3,CMan who set up traps and explosives
OL,4,C'inspired by Home Alone'
OL,6,FOpening the couple's trial on
OL,7,FThursday, 23 October, prosecutor Helen
OL,8,FChapman told a jury that officers
OL,9,Ffound weapons including a home-made
OL,10,Fflamethrower, large quantities of
OL,11,Fcannabis, amphetamines and cash, as
OL,12,Fwell as a series of traps.
OL,14,FShe told the jurors: "If you are
OL,15,Fsitting there thinking that this
OL,16,Fsounds a little like the film Home
OL,17,FAlone, then you would be correct.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/9
