OL,3,CMan who set up traps and explosives
OL,4,C'inspired by Home Alone'
OL,6,F"In fact that is precisely what Ian
OL,7,FClaughton said he was aiming for when
OL,8,Fhe told the police about these
OL,9,Fdevices."
OL,11,FMs Chapman told the court: "When the
OL,12,Fpolice attended at those addresses and
OL,13,Fexecuted those warrants, what they
OL,14,Ffound were properties which were
OL,15,Fheavily protected.
OL,17,F"They needed to be heavily protected,
OL,18,Fthe prosecution say, because they were
OL,19,Ffull of drugs and cash."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/9
