OL,4,C'inspired by Home Alone'
OL,6,FOther devices found in the property
OL,7,Fcomprised of banger fireworks inside
OL,8,Fpiping, sealed with foam, and with
OL,9,Fwires and a coiled spring.
OL,11,FThe prosecutor told the jury of seven
OL,12,Fwomen and five men that a stun gun was
OL,13,Ffound behind a fridge-freezer and a
OL,14,Fhomemade flame-thrower was discovered
OL,15,Fin a workshop.
OL,17,FShe said it was a fire extinguisher
OL,18,Ffilled with petrol, which had been
OL,19,Fadapted so fuel would be emitted at
OL,20,Fpressure.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/9
