OL,6,FOther weapons found at the properties
OL,7,Fincluded two high-powered air guns and
OL,8,Fa crossbow.
OL,10,FMs Chapman said the cash found in the
OL,11,Fproperty included #27,000 sewn into a
OL,12,Fsettee.
OL,14,FCannabis plants were found growing in
OL,15,Ftwo of the houses, including some in
OL,16,Ftents in hidden rooms.
