OL,6,FThe prosecutor told the jury that
OL,7,Fofficers went to the three houses,
OL,8,Fwhich are next door to each other,
OL,9,Fafter Border Force found a package of
OL,10,Fimitation firearms ordered from China,
OL,11,Faddressed to Lesley Claughton.
OL,13,FThe package was opened at Heathrow
OL,14,FAirport and five small silver-and-
OL,15,Fblack folding five-shot revolvers were
OL,16,Ffound.
OL,18,FIan Claughton, 60, denies possession
OL,19,Fof prohibited firearms, criminal
OL,20,Fproperty and an explosive substance.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/9
